name: Data for Figure 2 (Early vs Late Evoked Timing)
citation: Liu, Benjamin (2024) Data for Figure 2 (Early vs Late Evoked Timing) (Version draft) [Data set]. DANDI archive. https://dandiarchive.org/dandiset/001096/draft
description: The mat file contains the necessary data to create Figure 2 of the paper, which is one of the key findings of the study. The data is contained in a MATLAB structure and has the relevant labels for the type of training performed, cell-type, stimulation used, raw data traces, and averaged data traces.
